name: Failed Switch
description:
This game made for 72h Wowie GameJam 3.0 : https://itch.io/jam/wowie-jam-3
With the theme : Failure is Progress

Your mission is get to the big green square, avoid get catch by other pink circle, switching your corpse like a ghost, get through yellow laser by hacking your mind, let's see what you can do =))

THIS GAME MADE FOR EPIC GAMER ONLY !
